1
00:01:28,970 --> 00:01:34,990
(The Wind Blows from Longxi)

2
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:37,900
(The Eighteenth Strategy Interlocked Stratagems)

3
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:38,950
Where are we?

4
00:01:38,950 --> 00:01:39,310
(Li Yan's Villa in Nanzheng County, the Shu State)
Where are we?

5
00:01:39,310 --> 00:01:39,680
(Li Yan's Villa in Nanzheng County, the Shu State)

6
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,280
Didn't you say General Li Yan asked to see me?
(Li Yan's Villa in Nanzheng County, the Shu State)

7
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:41,660
(Li Yan's Villa in Nanzheng County, the Shu State)

8
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:43,340
This is General Li Yan's villa.
(Li Yan's Villa in Nanzheng County, the Shu State)

9
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:45,509
He's waiting for you in Yangxin Chamber.

10
00:01:47,100 --> 00:01:47,780
I never expected to see

11
00:01:47,780 --> 00:01:49,580
such a beautiful house in Nanzheng County.

12
00:01:51,539 --> 00:01:52,259
Do you like it?

13
00:01:52,700 --> 00:01:53,729
Yes, of course.

14
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:55,490
If you like it,

15
00:01:55,850 --> 00:01:57,460
you can also move in.

16
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:58,400
Are you sure?

17
00:01:58,420 --> 00:01:59,000
Sure.

18
00:01:59,130 --> 00:02:00,300
Why would I lie to you?

19
00:02:03,690 --> 00:02:04,620
Thank you, Clerk Feng.

20
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:05,830
I'm quite happy.

21
00:02:06,390 --> 00:02:07,360
Are you insane?

22
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,720
You'll get me killed, you know?

23
00:02:12,470 --> 00:02:14,050
I'm sorry.

24
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,530
Be serious.

25
00:02:17,810 --> 00:02:18,740
I just don't know

26
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:20,140
what else I can do to thank you, Clerk Feng.

27
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:21,930
Please don't blame me.

28
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:26,860
If you can sometimes tell me

29
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:28,300
what you see and hear,

30
00:02:28,670 --> 00:02:29,990
you'll be expressing your gratitude.

31
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:32,220
Don't worry.

32
00:02:32,380 --> 00:02:33,780
I'm grateful to you.

33
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:36,200
I'll always be loyal to you, Clerk Feng.

34
00:02:39,420 --> 00:02:41,140
Unless you want to be killed,

35
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:43,870
keep such thoughts in your mind

36
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,200
and never bring them up again.

37
00:02:48,390 --> 00:02:49,430
I'll keep it in mind.

38
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:35,130
Bravo!

39
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:38,170
General, you played the song

40
00:03:38,350 --> 00:03:40,220
as well as the God of Zither.

41
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,130
It sounded so beautiful

42
00:03:45,540 --> 00:03:46,660
and no one could play better than you.

43
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,430
Miss Liu.

44
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:55,390
Miss Liu, you're my soul mate.

45
00:03:55,990 --> 00:03:57,190
Don't bother to kneel.

46
00:03:57,210 --> 00:03:57,910
You may rise.

47
00:03:57,940 --> 00:03:59,130
Come on. Get up.

48
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:00,140
Thank you, General.

49
00:04:00,140 --> 00:04:01,100
Come over. Come.

50
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:03,980
Feng Ying, you may rise, too.

51
00:04:04,540 --> 00:04:05,340
Feng Ying,

52
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:06,680
let's drink tonight.

53
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,390
I have something to tell you.

54
00:04:09,340 --> 00:04:10,500
Come over. Come.

55
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,300
I'll be waiting in the wing room.

56
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:15,860
Fieldwork spies got back some delicacies.

57
00:04:16,290 --> 00:04:17,610
The cook doesn't know how to cook them.

58
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,250
I'll go check it out in case they're wasted.

59
00:04:19,740 --> 00:04:20,700
Off you go.

60
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:22,920
Come on, Miss Liu. This way.

61
00:04:23,100 --> 00:04:23,860
Come in, please.

62
00:04:27,060 --> 00:04:28,780
Be seated.

63
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:30,570
I don't dare to sit here.

64
00:04:30,930 --> 00:04:32,000
Why?

65
00:04:32,170 --> 00:04:33,180
Just be seated. Come on.

66
00:04:33,980 --> 00:04:34,820
Thank you, General.

67
00:04:41,220 --> 00:04:43,530
Miss Liu, what do you think of this zither?

68
00:04:57,570 --> 00:04:58,860
Miss Liu,

69
00:04:59,460 --> 00:05:01,100
if you like it,

70
00:05:01,570 --> 00:05:04,030
why not have a try?

71
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:08,080
General, this is your treasure.

72
00:05:08,740 --> 00:05:10,970
I don't dare to use it.

73
00:05:11,970 --> 00:05:13,220
So what?

74
00:05:13,660 --> 00:05:15,870
You can use everything

75
00:05:16,130 --> 00:05:17,940
in this villa as you wish.

76
00:05:19,460 --> 00:05:20,340
Last time,

77
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,240
when I heard you play the song,

78
00:05:23,580 --> 00:05:26,490
I had strong feelings.

79
00:05:29,210 --> 00:05:30,040
So,

80
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:32,810
I wrote a poem

81
00:05:34,330 --> 00:05:35,780
for you.

82
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:46,200
If you can make it a song,

83
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:48,940
it'll be popular all over the country.

84
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:51,300
Green, green,

85
00:05:51,610 --> 00:05:53,159
the grass by the river.

86
00:05:54,540 --> 00:05:55,900
And in thought,

87
00:05:56,860 --> 00:05:58,460
I follow it far, far away.

88
00:05:59,230 --> 00:06:00,410
By hands,

89
00:06:00,670 --> 00:06:02,970
the zither is played.

90
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,320
I miss you

91
00:06:06,300 --> 00:06:08,180
every night.

92
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:16,780
How many soul mates can we have?

93
00:06:17,530 --> 00:06:18,490
I live

94
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:20,170
a wandering life.

95
00:06:21,150 --> 00:06:22,920
Luckily, I meet my soul mate.

96
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,790
I become

97
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:28,580
spirited again.

98
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:31,150
What a nice poem!

99
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:35,780
General, with civil and martial virtues,

100
00:06:36,100 --> 00:06:37,500
you're indeed the pillar of our state.

101
00:06:38,070 --> 00:06:39,980
The soul mate in this poem

102
00:06:42,010 --> 00:06:43,450
turns out to be you, Miss Liu.

103
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:49,390
Miss Liu,

104
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:50,840
what are you doing?

105
00:06:52,540 --> 00:06:54,330
My parents died when I was little.

106
00:06:55,980 --> 00:06:57,460
I've been living a wandering life.

107
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,590
Luckily, I met you, General.

108
00:07:04,090 --> 00:07:05,400
Hope you'll care about me.

109
00:07:12,470 --> 00:07:13,430
Miss Liu,

110
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:19,390
I will be with you

111
00:07:19,780 --> 00:07:21,250
till the end

112
00:07:22,020 --> 00:07:25,010
of the line.

113
00:07:30,470 --> 00:07:31,580
Thank you, General.

114
00:07:33,909 --> 00:07:39,980
(Xun Xu's House in Nanzheng County, the Shu State)

115
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:46,840
Zhulong's Case

116
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,880
has reverberated throughout the state.

117
00:07:49,730 --> 00:07:51,380
The court is also concerned about it.

118
00:07:53,170 --> 00:07:53,850
Yeah.

119
00:07:54,300 --> 00:07:55,250
Gao Tangbing

120
00:07:55,780 --> 00:07:57,100
wouldn't work alone.

121
00:07:57,740 --> 00:08:01,860
Clerk Feng's oversight of his supervisory duty was pardoned.

122
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:05,280
Looks like the court doesn't want too many people to be involved.

123
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:11,900
This isn't our concern.

124
00:08:13,130 --> 00:08:14,170
As far as I see,

125
00:08:14,790 --> 00:08:17,640
this case must be completely revealed.

126
00:08:18,780 --> 00:08:20,420
Otherwise, I wouldn't live up

127
00:08:20,420 --> 00:08:21,730
to my job in the Internal Affairs Department.

128
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,130
But Xun Xu,

129
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,510
I'm worried

130
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:26,260
when the case is revealed

131
00:08:27,460 --> 00:08:28,540
you can't imagine

132
00:08:31,780 --> 00:08:32,730
how much pressure you're going to bear.

133
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:36,390
I think after you became the Chief Clerk,

134
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:38,140
you started to care about your post.

135
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,850
We're buddies.

136
00:08:42,650 --> 00:08:43,690
I'm caring about it for your sake.

137
00:08:44,100 --> 00:08:44,980
Think about it.

138
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,430
Gao Tangbing

139
00:08:46,810 --> 00:08:49,210
worked in the Intelligence Analysis Department for seven or eight years.

140
00:08:49,650 --> 00:08:50,650
He knew

141
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:51,760
a big bunch of people.

142
00:08:51,860 --> 00:08:52,500
I believe the superiors

143
00:08:52,500 --> 00:08:54,140
don't want you to expose the case too much.

144
00:08:57,610 --> 00:08:58,940
I'm no longer young.

145
00:09:00,170 --> 00:09:02,180
All I want is to follow my conscience.

146
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,170
How old are you?

147
00:09:04,190 --> 00:09:05,300
No longer young?

148
00:09:09,450 --> 00:09:11,340
I've got a kind of feeling.

149
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:14,720
If I can find out the truth of Zhulong's Case,

150
00:09:15,610 --> 00:09:17,140
my life will be worthwhile.

151
00:09:18,620 --> 00:09:19,540
What's wrong with you?

152
00:09:19,570 --> 00:09:21,080
Why do you keep saying that?

153
00:09:21,260 --> 00:09:22,460
You still have a long way to go.

154
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:26,140
Clerk Chen, Chief Xun,

155
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:26,950
something happened.

156
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:27,910
What happened?

157
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:30,190
Gao Tangbing killed himself.

158
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:38,270
Cheers, General.

159
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,360
I sent Miss Liu

160
00:09:45,820 --> 00:09:46,700
to pack her things.

161
00:09:48,230 --> 00:09:49,240
In a couple of days,

162
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:51,750
let her move in.

163
00:09:52,220 --> 00:09:54,340
Ziyan House lies in a disreputable place.

164
00:09:54,660 --> 00:09:56,820
Miss Liu shouldn't always live there.

165
00:09:58,540 --> 00:09:59,940
Feng Ying,

166
00:10:00,740 --> 00:10:02,020
these are only trifles.

167
00:10:02,620 --> 00:10:04,500
I'll have you take care of them.

168
00:10:05,550 --> 00:10:06,140
Rest assured.

169
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:08,040
I will have everything arranged perfectly.

170
00:10:09,300 --> 00:10:12,420
Only in this way can I feel relieved.

171
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,120
Feng Ying,

172
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:15,810
I only did a little favor

173
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,470
to help you out of trouble.

174
00:10:23,170 --> 00:10:25,290
General, you think it's a little favor.

175
00:10:25,890 --> 00:10:26,970
But in my heart,

176
00:10:27,700 --> 00:10:29,020
you saved my life.

177
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:30,830
I'm a clumsy man.

178
00:10:31,070 --> 00:10:33,870
But I never hesitate about repaying you.

179
00:10:34,330 --> 00:10:35,460
Get up. Get up.

180
00:10:36,690 --> 00:10:39,060
I have a selfish motive

181
00:10:39,890 --> 00:10:41,330
to keep you in Siwencao Intelligence.

182
00:10:43,220 --> 00:10:44,100
I'm all ears, General.

183
00:10:45,900 --> 00:10:46,260
Come over.

184
00:10:51,620 --> 00:10:53,340
At the morning court in Chengdu,

185
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:56,100
Zhuge Liang and I

186
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:57,660
got incompatible.

187
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,250
We will break with each other sooner or later.

188
00:11:00,050 --> 00:11:01,050
Rest assured, General.

189
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,280
Now that I'm on your side,

190
00:11:03,830 --> 00:11:05,400
I owe my life to you.

191
00:11:06,220 --> 00:11:07,620
No matter how dangerous my mission is,

192
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:09,760
I will not decline it.

193
00:11:16,250 --> 00:11:17,500
His Majesty gave me a secret edict.

194
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,520
Now that you have it,

195
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:23,700
what are you scared of?

196
00:11:24,020 --> 00:11:25,340
I have a secret edict.

197
00:11:25,850 --> 00:11:28,740
But Zhuge Liang has great power in the court

198
00:11:29,180 --> 00:11:30,500
and he can't be underestimated.

199
00:11:32,410 --> 00:11:33,060
That's right.

200
00:11:34,620 --> 00:11:35,740
Speaking of that,

201
00:11:36,490 --> 00:11:38,100
except for local clans,

202
00:11:38,780 --> 00:11:40,650
most civil and military officials

203
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:42,950
were instructed by the Prime Minister.

204
00:11:42,970 --> 00:11:44,080
So,

205
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:47,210
we mustn't leave any trace!

206
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:51,510
We have to prove his crime of deceiving His Majesty

207
00:11:51,530 --> 00:11:53,970
and let no one realize that it's our trap.

208
00:11:58,930 --> 00:11:59,760
Got it, General.

209
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:01,540
When I have a detailed plan,

210
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:03,140
I'll let you know.

211
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:07,880
Feng Ying,

212
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:10,940
I count on you

213
00:12:11,830 --> 00:12:15,300
for the fate of our state.

214
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:21,190
I won't let you down, General.

215
00:12:28,770 --> 00:12:30,060
After dinner last night,

216
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:32,190
no one came.

217
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:34,940
They didn't find out that Gao Tangbing died

218
00:12:35,410 --> 00:12:37,450
until they patrolled at eleven.

219
00:12:41,660 --> 00:12:42,420
Impossible.

220
00:12:43,090 --> 00:12:44,250
This is impossible.

221
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:47,130
A wood chip from the table leg killed him.

222
00:12:57,940 --> 00:12:59,060
The wood chip

223
00:13:00,050 --> 00:13:01,660
penetrated his neck.

224
00:13:03,700 --> 00:13:04,700
According to the preliminary judgment,

225
00:13:07,160 --> 00:13:08,050
he killed himself.

226
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:38,790
Xun Xu,

227
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:41,680
don't lose heart.

228
00:13:42,250 --> 00:13:43,280
Actually,

229
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:45,740
it may be a good thing.

230
00:13:49,940 --> 00:13:50,660
I'm serious.

231
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:57,770
This is a great thing.

232
00:13:58,400 --> 00:14:00,080
When Xun Xu keeps investigating the case,

233
00:14:00,660 --> 00:14:03,100
everybody is gossiping fiercely.

234
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:04,630
About what?

235
00:14:05,890 --> 00:14:08,330
They say Xun Xu wants

236
00:14:08,830 --> 00:14:10,550
to investigate all seniors like us

237
00:14:10,570 --> 00:14:11,760
for his own self-interest.

238
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:18,200
To catch Zhulong,

239
00:14:18,620 --> 00:14:20,270
Chief Xun paid a big price.

240
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:23,120
Stop gossiping about him.

241
00:14:25,230 --> 00:14:25,840
Yes.

242
00:14:26,420 --> 00:14:27,540
You're right, Clerk Feng.

243
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,480
So,

244
00:14:28,690 --> 00:14:30,140
I stopped them

245
00:14:30,140 --> 00:14:31,020
from gossiping immediately.

246
00:14:31,150 --> 00:14:31,740
I told them

247
00:14:31,810 --> 00:14:33,490
that they should give priority to

248
00:14:33,490 --> 00:14:35,140
the work of the Internal Affairs Department.

249
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:37,340
Feng Ying,

250
00:14:37,670 --> 00:14:39,590
they have a reason to gossip.

251
00:14:40,010 --> 00:14:42,020
Xun Xu keeps picking on Gao Tangbing.

252
00:14:42,410 --> 00:14:43,490
He must be up to something.

253
00:14:44,040 --> 00:14:45,410
Xun Xu is

254
00:14:45,740 --> 00:14:47,380
paralyzed from the waist down

255
00:14:47,930 --> 00:14:49,740
so that he's like a changed man.

256
00:14:50,110 --> 00:14:51,830
Feng Ying, he hates you.

257
00:14:51,860 --> 00:14:52,980
Don't talk nonsense!

258
00:14:53,700 --> 00:14:55,060
It's not nonsense. It's the truth.

259
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:55,730
Stop.

260
00:14:58,820 --> 00:14:59,860
Don't talk nonsense when you're at work.

261
00:15:00,190 --> 00:15:02,830
I'll have a word with Xun Xu.

262
00:15:06,370 --> 00:15:07,060
Aye.

263
00:15:12,010 --> 00:15:13,330
Gao Tangbing is dead.

264
00:15:13,690 --> 00:15:15,900
Zhulong's Case can finally be closed.

265
00:15:17,830 --> 00:15:18,560
Chen Gong,

266
00:15:19,940 --> 00:15:21,460
a lot of people are involved in this case.

267
00:15:21,460 --> 00:15:22,420
It's not that simple.

268
00:15:24,980 --> 00:15:25,820
I'm certainly aware of that.

269
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:34,040
But closing the case as a suicide

270
00:15:34,820 --> 00:15:35,740
will be advantageous to you.

271
00:15:36,410 --> 00:15:37,220
Do as I tell you.

272
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:53,060
Gao Tangbing wouldn't kill himself.

273
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:55,880
We had him checked several times.

274
00:15:56,700 --> 00:15:59,690
The angle, strength of the wood chip,

275
00:16:00,380 --> 00:16:03,060
and even the spraying direction of blood all coincided.

276
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:04,860
He killed himself, I guess.

277
00:16:06,810 --> 00:16:08,000
I know him very well.

278
00:16:08,680 --> 00:16:10,250
He isn't that kind of man who would kill himself.

279
00:16:15,190 --> 00:16:17,000
The wood chip was taken from the table leg.

280
00:16:17,260 --> 00:16:18,470
But his hand was clean.

281
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:19,820
It wasn't even scratched.

282
00:16:20,590 --> 00:16:21,260
So, it wasn't him

283
00:16:21,260 --> 00:16:22,980
who took the wood chip off the table leg.

284
00:16:23,560 --> 00:16:24,680
If so,

285
00:16:25,280 --> 00:16:27,230
the murderer must have made a noise.

