00:30:57,780 --> 00:30:58,750
That's for sure.

570
00:31:00,350 --> 00:31:02,240
If Li Yan dares to activate this plan,

571
00:31:03,640 --> 00:31:04,680
he will be

572
00:31:05,390 --> 00:31:07,400
on his way to death.

573
00:31:10,310 --> 00:31:11,600
I'm always reassured about you.

574
00:31:14,730 --> 00:31:16,020
But in this way,

575
00:31:17,700 --> 00:31:18,610
I'm afraid

576
00:31:19,030 --> 00:31:20,350
you can't get away.

577
00:31:21,490 --> 00:31:22,720
Even if I die,

578
00:31:23,660 --> 00:31:24,670
the Shu State will last.

579
00:31:25,410 --> 00:31:26,620
I'll have no regrets.

580
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:39,080
Is there anything else

581
00:31:39,520 --> 00:31:41,370
I can help you with?

582
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,080
Yes.

583
00:31:44,660 --> 00:31:46,260
There're two problems in Siwencao Intelligence

584
00:31:46,560 --> 00:31:47,540
that I can hardly handle.

585
00:31:49,090 --> 00:31:50,260
Chen Gong?

586
00:31:50,370 --> 00:31:51,050
Right.

587
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:53,770
Chen Gong hates you

588
00:31:54,090 --> 00:31:56,330
for his father's death ten years ago.

589
00:31:56,850 --> 00:31:57,770
I can explain it to him

590
00:31:57,770 --> 00:31:59,130
when possible.

591
00:32:01,630 --> 00:32:02,710
What is the other problem?

592
00:32:03,550 --> 00:32:04,500
Xun Xu.

593
00:32:05,840 --> 00:32:07,270
He's sticking to the case,

594
00:32:07,790 --> 00:32:09,260
much faster than my schedule.

595
00:32:10,820 --> 00:32:12,670
He doesn't let go of Gao Tangbing's death.

596
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:14,660
Soon, he'll track down on me.

597
00:32:16,730 --> 00:32:18,530
I'm afraid I can't hold onto the last minute.

598
00:32:21,850 --> 00:32:22,800
Stop the investigation?

599
00:32:24,380 --> 00:32:25,340
Precisely,

600
00:32:26,250 --> 00:32:27,820
I must close the case as a suicide

601
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:29,440
and investigate it secretly.

602
00:32:30,690 --> 00:32:32,130
Everybody in the Agency is experienced.

603
00:32:32,730 --> 00:32:35,170
We'll easily be exposed even if we investigate secretly.

604
00:32:35,350 --> 00:32:36,230
How can we carry on?

605
00:32:38,890 --> 00:32:39,890
Tell me again

606
00:32:40,340 --> 00:32:41,550
about what happened

607
00:32:41,570 --> 00:32:42,490
when Gao Tangbing died.

608
00:32:43,710 --> 00:32:44,740
Last night,

609
00:32:45,110 --> 00:32:46,680
I was on duty.

610
00:32:48,320 --> 00:32:49,250
Come on. Time for the roll call.

611
00:32:49,250 --> 00:32:51,420
When we changed shifts at eleven,

612
00:32:52,050 --> 00:32:53,180
according to the rules,

613
00:32:53,390 --> 00:32:54,470
two persons were patrolling.

614
00:32:55,320 --> 00:32:56,040
Time for the roll call.

615
00:33:07,610 --> 00:33:08,290
Chief Gao.

616
00:33:08,660 --> 00:33:09,700
Chief Gao, time for the roll call.

617
00:33:10,300 --> 00:33:11,090
Chief Gao?

618
00:33:24,390 --> 00:33:25,260
Chief Gao.

619
00:33:27,420 --> 00:33:28,270
Chief Gao?

620
00:33:31,760 --> 00:33:32,440
Oh, no.

621
00:33:39,710 --> 00:33:41,320
When I reached the cell,

622
00:33:42,300 --> 00:33:43,860
Gao Tangbing died a long time ago.

623
00:33:45,370 --> 00:33:46,530
When was dinner sent to him?

624
00:33:46,780 --> 00:33:47,580
It was recorded.

625
00:33:47,990 --> 00:33:48,990
At a quarter past five.

626
00:33:49,300 --> 00:33:50,340
He was alive at that time.

627
00:33:50,900 --> 00:33:52,170
Did you ask the deliveryman?

628
00:33:52,650 --> 00:33:53,480
Yes.

629
00:33:53,900 --> 00:33:54,710
He said

630
00:33:55,230 --> 00:33:57,040
Chief Gao looked a little bit dispirited

631
00:33:57,260 --> 00:33:58,300
and nothing else was unusual.

632
00:34:04,030 --> 00:34:05,030
So,

633
00:34:06,150 --> 00:34:08,040
whether he killed himself or was killed,

634
00:34:08,550 --> 00:34:10,600
it happened between a quarter past five

635
00:34:10,630 --> 00:34:11,670
to eleven.

636
00:34:12,020 --> 00:34:12,739
Right.

637
00:34:13,130 --> 00:34:14,580
Within the five hours.

638
00:34:14,929 --> 00:34:15,969
During that period,

639
00:34:16,780 --> 00:34:18,290
no one went in or out of his jail.

640
00:34:20,630 --> 00:34:22,199
Gao Tangbing is a felon.

641
00:34:22,570 --> 00:34:23,889
The last door of his jail can't be opened

642
00:34:23,980 --> 00:34:25,940
without two keys.

643
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:28,989
It was immensely difficult

644
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,929
to sneak into his jail without leaving a trace.

645
00:34:35,659 --> 00:34:36,489
Feng Ying,

646
00:34:38,060 --> 00:34:39,139
I'll count on you.

647
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:40,600
Don't worry, Yang Yi.

648
00:34:41,929 --> 00:34:42,460
Farewell.

649
00:34:54,670 --> 00:34:55,940
It's okay. Get to your business.

650
00:34:55,969 --> 00:34:56,690
Umm...

651
00:34:57,060 --> 00:34:57,550
Feng Ying...

652
00:34:57,570 --> 00:34:58,980
What? Stop prevaricating.

653
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:03,080
I'm afraid Chief Yang's visit

654
00:35:03,380 --> 00:35:04,820
will be disadvantageous to you.

655
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:09,260
Don't tell anyone

656
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:11,440
that Chief Yang visited me.

657
00:35:12,150 --> 00:35:13,350
You shall forget it, too.

658
00:35:13,950 --> 00:35:15,400
But I'm worried about you.

659
00:35:16,080 --> 00:35:16,910
Think about it.

660
00:35:17,570 --> 00:35:19,170
Shortly after you sold him out,

661
00:35:19,190 --> 00:35:20,910
he came to visit you.

662
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:22,210
He must be up to something.

663
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:25,120
You don't know

664
00:35:25,590 --> 00:35:26,550
about politics.

665
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:28,210
Don't try to interfere.

666
00:35:29,680 --> 00:35:32,110
General Li Yan is irreconcilable with Yang Yi.

667
00:35:33,050 --> 00:35:35,010
You must be very careful.

668
00:35:40,990 --> 00:35:41,470
Mm.

669
00:35:43,390 --> 00:35:44,080
I understand.

670
00:35:55,110 --> 00:35:56,000
Greetings, General.

671
00:35:59,000 --> 00:35:59,680
Clerk Chen.

672
00:35:59,970 --> 00:36:00,580
Clerk Feng.

673
00:36:00,600 --> 00:36:01,450
Be seated.

674
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:09,830
Feng Ying,

675
00:36:10,790 --> 00:36:11,900
you're late.

676
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:14,720
There was some urgent work to handle

677
00:36:15,450 --> 00:36:16,540
and I was held up.

678
00:36:17,530 --> 00:36:18,860
The Northern Expedition is starting soon.

679
00:36:19,070 --> 00:36:21,110
I've got a secret edict.

680
00:36:21,630 --> 00:36:24,920
I told Feng Ying about the key points.

681
00:36:26,330 --> 00:36:27,080
Feng Ying,

682
00:36:27,430 --> 00:36:28,680
have you got an idea?

683
00:36:28,990 --> 00:36:29,860
Tell us about it.

684
00:36:38,110 --> 00:36:39,870
Chen Gong is the son of my friend.

685
00:36:41,300 --> 00:36:42,290
He's an insider.

686
00:36:42,870 --> 00:36:43,590
I know.

687
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:45,250
I don't mean that.

688
00:36:47,230 --> 00:36:48,510
This room is heavily guarded.

689
00:36:48,750 --> 00:36:49,790
It's absolutely safe.

690
00:36:49,830 --> 00:36:51,110
Don't worry, Clerk Feng.

691
00:36:52,910 --> 00:36:53,360
Mm.

692
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:59,920
General, you told me

693
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:01,960
that we needed

694
00:37:02,460 --> 00:37:03,930
to complete two missions.

695
00:37:04,700 --> 00:37:05,420
First,

696
00:37:05,770 --> 00:37:06,880
the second Northern Expedition

697
00:37:07,380 --> 00:37:08,510
would waste our national strength

698
00:37:08,910 --> 00:37:10,100
and bring harm to our state.

699
00:37:10,970 --> 00:37:13,730
His Majesty wants to make the Prime Minister fail secretly.

700
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:14,970
Second,

701
00:37:16,020 --> 00:37:17,040
General shouldn't

702
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:19,920
get involved in this action.

703
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:22,890
Otherwise, once we fail,

704
00:37:23,580 --> 00:37:24,270
we will

705
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:26,920
shoot ourselves in the foot.

706
00:37:27,570 --> 00:37:28,430
Feng Ying,

707
00:37:29,860 --> 00:37:31,730
good points.

708
00:37:33,410 --> 00:37:34,740
It's quite a difficult mission.

709
00:37:35,700 --> 00:37:36,440
Clerk Feng,

710
00:37:37,660 --> 00:37:38,610
do you have any good ideas?

711
00:37:39,270 --> 00:37:40,630
Now that it's a mission for me,

712
00:37:41,030 --> 00:37:42,640
I have to try it, however difficult it is.

713
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:45,880
Feng Ying, are you saying

714
00:37:46,350 --> 00:37:47,860
that you've already got a good idea?

715
00:37:48,490 --> 00:37:49,330
I have

716
00:37:49,860 --> 00:37:51,060
interlocked stratagems.

717
00:37:52,130 --> 00:37:53,400
Three steps are needed.

718
00:37:58,480 --> 00:37:59,880
Let's drink

719
00:38:01,050 --> 00:38:03,210
before Feng Ying explains it.

720
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:14,560
There are three steps.

721
00:38:14,990 --> 00:38:17,030
But the point is simple.

722
00:38:18,240 --> 00:38:19,070
Making use of someone else.

723
00:38:21,850 --> 00:38:23,380
I'm all ears.

724
00:38:24,530 --> 00:38:26,580
For the Northern Expedition,

725
00:38:26,970 --> 00:38:29,620
the Prime Minister will imitate Han Xin's trick

726
00:38:29,640 --> 00:38:31,040
to carry on a secret affair.

727
00:38:32,250 --> 00:38:36,010
Wei Yan and his army will fake an attack on Longxi through Mount Qi.

728
00:38:37,780 --> 00:38:38,730
The Prime Minister himself

729
00:38:39,590 --> 00:38:41,910
will attack Chencang County unexpectedly

730
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:43,730
with the main force.

731
00:38:44,560 --> 00:38:47,210
With Chencang County as the transfer center for army provisions,

732
00:38:47,230 --> 00:38:48,700
they'll approach Chang'an.

733
00:38:50,070 --> 00:38:51,360
So, the first step,

734
00:38:52,130 --> 00:38:53,580
we can disclose this secret

735
00:38:54,150 --> 00:38:55,400
to the Wei Army

736
00:38:56,610 --> 00:38:59,540
so that they will wipe out Wei Yan's army.

737
00:39:02,440 --> 00:39:03,520
Even if

738
00:39:05,310 --> 00:39:07,060
Wei Yan's vanguard

739
00:39:08,090 --> 00:39:09,290
can be all killed,

740
00:39:10,310 --> 00:39:11,670
it may not harm

741
00:39:12,250 --> 00:39:13,690
the Northern Expedition.

742
00:39:14,380 --> 00:39:15,380
This is only the first step.

743
00:39:16,540 --> 00:39:17,940
It aims

744
00:39:18,610 --> 00:39:20,100
to hold up the Prime Minister

745
00:39:20,410 --> 00:39:21,320
so that

746
00:39:21,420 --> 00:39:23,050
he can't conquer Chencang County

747
00:39:23,570 --> 00:39:25,000
and it will gain time

748
00:39:25,450 --> 00:39:26,300
for our second step.

749
00:39:32,990 --> 00:39:33,800
Sir,

750
00:39:35,200 --> 00:39:37,510
there are two difficulties

751
00:39:38,170 --> 00:39:39,380
to carry out this plan.

752
00:39:40,590 --> 00:39:41,440
Be specific.

753
00:39:41,750 --> 00:39:42,620
First,

754
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:44,670
the Prime Minister's plan

755
00:39:45,240 --> 00:39:46,200
to attack Chencang County secretly

756
00:39:46,840 --> 00:39:47,920
must be a top secret.

757
00:39:49,530 --> 00:39:52,060
The transmission of intel is complicated.

758
00:39:52,590 --> 00:39:53,590
What if...

759
00:39:53,620 --> 00:39:55,590
I mean what if the intel is intercepted by our spies?

760
00:39:56,320 --> 00:39:57,610
Once they investigate it,

761
00:39:57,920 --> 00:39:59,430
they will soon track down us.

762
00:39:59,630 --> 00:40:00,350
Sir,

763
00:40:02,890 --> 00:40:03,820
then you'll be accused

764
00:40:04,250 --> 00:40:05,250
of treason.

765
00:40:07,200 --> 00:40:07,920
Second,

766
00:40:09,720 --> 00:40:11,040
the intelligence systems of Shu and Wei

767
00:40:11,130 --> 00:40:12,100
can be very complicated.

768
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:13,190
Some intel is real while some is false.

769
00:40:13,950 --> 00:40:14,760
Clerk Feng,

770
00:40:15,930 --> 00:40:17,370
how can you guarantee

771
00:40:17,810 --> 00:40:19,680
that senior management of Wei

772
00:40:19,700 --> 00:40:21,230
will believe the intel

773
00:40:21,580 --> 00:40:22,210
we tell them?

774
00:40:32,930 --> 00:40:33,840
This isn't a problem.

775
00:40:36,450 --> 00:40:37,090
I have

776
00:40:38,010 --> 00:40:39,650
an intelligence channel

777
00:40:39,680 --> 00:40:40,650
to contact Guo Huai directly.

778
00:40:41,570 --> 00:40:42,480
He will believe it.

779
00:40:43,090 --> 00:40:44,150
I never expected you

780
00:40:45,460 --> 00:40:47,670
to have such a high-level intelligence channel.

781
00:40:49,820 --> 00:40:50,620
Feng Ying,

782
00:40:52,410 --> 00:40:54,340
you're awesome!

783
00:40:55,340 --> 00:40:56,020
General,

784
00:40:56,920 --> 00:40:58,130
to restore the Han Dynasty,

785
00:40:58,570 --> 00:40:59,500
our agency

786
00:40:59,910 --> 00:41:01,630
has to adopt some extreme measures.

787
00:41:06,560 --> 00:41:07,080
Sir,

788
00:41:08,170 --> 00:41:09,700
if Clerk Feng can send this intel

789
00:41:09,700 --> 00:41:10,770
to Guo Huai

790
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:11,670
straightforwardly,

791
00:41:12,200 --> 00:41:12,710
this plan

792
00:41:13,780 --> 00:41:14,370
will be feasible.

793
00:41:16,350 --> 00:41:17,260
Second,

794
00:41:18,520 --> 00:41:20,450
we have to count on you, General.

795
00:41:22,200 --> 00:41:24,920
The late emperor ordered you to garrison Jiangzhou for a long time

796
00:41:25,190 --> 00:41:26,030
against the Wu Army.

797
00:41:28,390 --> 00:41:30,020
So, Clerk Feng, it's the Wu Army

798
00:41:30,020 --> 00:41:30,930
that you want to make use of.

799
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:33,440
Chen Gong, you're an insider.

800
00:41:33,880 --> 00:41:34,730
You got to understand me so quickly.

801
00:41:39,360 --> 00:41:40,960
In the second step,

802
00:41:41,770 --> 00:41:43,410
General, ask your henchmen

803
00:41:43,670 --> 00:41:44,660
to disguise themselves as the Wu soldiers,

804
00:41:45,050 --> 00:41:46,570
attack our checkpoints,

805
00:41:47,120 --> 00:41:48,560
and cut off the trade route between Wu and Shu.

806
00:41:48,960 --> 00:41:49,880
Then, let them spread rumors

807
00:41:50,240 --> 00:41:51,640
that the Wu Army will invade us

808
00:41:52,570 --> 00:41:55,030
and fake a huge crisis

809
00:41:55,050 --> 00:41:57,290
that we have to fight two states at the same time.

810
00:41:57,840 --> 00:41:58,750
However,

811
00:42:00,010 --> 00:42:01,260
the Wu State

812
00:42:02,030 --> 00:42:03,360
agreed to fight against the Wei Army

813
00:42:03,890 --> 00:42:05,060
together with our prime minister.

814
00:42:05,530 --> 00:42:06,750
Emperor Sun Quan of Wu

815
00:42:07,100 --> 00:42:08,110
will go to Wancheng County

816
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:10,810
with his army.

817
00:42:12,100 --> 00:42:13,390
How will he come to invade us?

818
00:42:14,350 --> 00:42:15,350
In war, there's always too much deception.

819
00:42:21,170 --> 00:42:23,120
Clerk Feng, are you saying

820
00:42:23,740 --> 00:42:24,660
that

821
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:27,320
the invasion of Wu

822
00:42:27,600 --> 00:42:28,810
doesn't need to be real?

823
00:42:29,230 --> 00:42:30,700
When the news gets to Chengdu

824
00:42:30,990 --> 00:42:33,160
and the Prime Minister isn't there,

825
00:42:33,390 --> 00:42:35,760
His Majesty will order General Li

826
00:42:35,920 --> 00:42:37,000
to negotiate with the Wu Army

827
00:42:38,550 --> 00:42:39,630
for final decision.

828
00:42:40,400 --> 00:42:41,030
That's right.

829
00:42:42,010 --> 00:42:42,970
His Majesty will do that.

830
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:45,120
In this way,

831
00:42:46,380 --> 00:42:48,420
I can withdraw

832
00:42:49,330 --> 00:42:51,280
the army provisions

833
00:42:51,760 --> 00:42:52,710
in the name of preparing to fight against Wu

834
00:42:53,130 --> 00:42:54,570
and have them sent to the frontline against Wu.

835
00:42:54,930 --> 00:42:56,210
This is drastic.

836
00:42:58,450 --> 00:42:59,930
But this is treason!

837
00:43:01,950 --> 00:43:03,040
It's wise of you, General.

