00:43:20,580 --> 00:43:21,420
So,

841
00:43:22,430 --> 00:43:23,720
my brother-in-law Feng Ying

842
00:43:24,120 --> 00:43:26,440
always knows the real Qingping Plan.

843
00:43:27,300 --> 00:43:29,020
He just cooperated with Yang Yi

844
00:43:29,420 --> 00:43:31,100
and set a trap for Li Yan by the way.

845
00:43:31,610 --> 00:43:34,130
He will overthrow Li Yan with three-step interlocked stratagems.

846
00:43:35,040 --> 00:43:36,040
Most ruthlessly,

847
00:43:36,100 --> 00:43:36,820
in the first step,

848
00:43:37,270 --> 00:43:39,560
Feng Ying gets himself involved.

849
00:43:40,440 --> 00:43:41,350
I guess it's because

850
00:43:41,370 --> 00:43:42,980
he still appears to work for Li Yan.

851
00:43:43,010 --> 00:43:44,440
He can't make Li Yan trust him

852
00:43:44,460 --> 00:43:46,260
unless he sacrifices first.

853
00:43:47,130 --> 00:43:48,000
Next,

854
00:43:48,540 --> 00:43:52,180
Li Yan will fake the truth that the Wu Army will invade us.

855
00:43:52,680 --> 00:43:56,000
Then the third step can be carried out logically.

856
00:43:56,620 --> 00:44:00,060
Li Yan will withdraw the army provisions from the frontline against Wei

857
00:44:00,350 --> 00:44:01,390
